<!-- *****************************  frontier squid attributes      **************************************** -->
<section id="customizing-squid-attrs-osg" xreflabel="Customizing OSG squid attrs">
<title>Customizing Squid attrs</title>

<para>
Attributes used to configure frontier squid.
</para>

<para>

<table frame='all'><title>Attributes Used in OSG Roll Frontier Squid Customization</title>
<tgroup cols='2' align='left' colsep='1' rowsep='1'>
<thead>
<row>
  <entry align="center">Attibute Name</entry>
  <entry align="center">Description</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_SquidCacheMem
</entry>
<entry>
Set squid cache memory. If not set rocks command will set to '512 MB'. 
Rpm install default is '128 MB'.
Default: node
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_SquidCacheDir
</entry>
<entry>
Set squid cache dir. If not set will use '/var/cache/squid'
Default: none
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_SquidCacheDirSize
</entry>
<entry>
Set cache dir size.If not set will use '10000' (10GB). 
Default: none
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_SQUID_OPEN_NETWORK
</entry>
<entry>
Set network allowed in firewall for monitoring purposes (udp port 3401) in firewall rule A20-SQUID-UDP-PORT. If not set will use '128.142.0.0/16,188.184.128.0/17,188.185.128.0/17'. 
Default: none
</entry>
</row>



</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>

</para>

</section>

